and fainting spells.

1054
01:13:44,468 --> 01:13:47,054
Her heart.
And intracranial hypertension.

1055
01:13:48,097 --> 01:13:49,485
In her head, yes.

1056
01:13:50,516 --> 01:13:53,197
No, it's in a more difficult area.

1057
01:13:53,894 --> 01:13:55,187
We don't know yet.

1058
01:13:55,396 --> 01:13:56,238
Dad!

1059
01:13:56,647 --> 01:13:59,032
I'll call from my phone in a moment.

1060
01:13:59,483 --> 01:14:01,156
No, she'll wake up.

1061
01:14:01,527 --> 01:14:03,200
I gave her a shot.

1062
01:14:04,613 --> 01:14:06,832
As you wish. Yes.

1063
01:14:07,325 --> 01:14:08,748
What's this, Mum?

1064
01:14:09,285 --> 01:14:10,708
Do you want to scare us?

1065
01:14:20,796 --> 01:14:22,386
Let's go, it's late.

1066
01:14:22,965 --> 01:14:24,057
I'm staying.

1067
01:14:24,967 --> 01:14:26,937
Eliza, Grandma's OK now.

1068
01:14:27,428 --> 01:14:29,765
What's intracranial hypertension?

1069
01:14:33,434 --> 01:14:35,771
It's a sort of pressure on the brain.

1070
01:14:35,978 --> 01:14:36,603
Depending on the area,
it can cause these episodes.

1071
01:14:36,604 --> 01:14:39,154
Depending on the area,
it can cause these episodes.

1072
01:14:40,107 --> 01:14:41,994
- Is it serious?
- Serious...

1073
01:14:42,610 --> 01:14:44,117
We'll see how it develops.

1074
01:14:44,320 --> 01:14:45,873
Why didn't you tell us?

1075
01:14:46,072 --> 01:14:47,365
Tell you what?

1076
01:14:47,573 --> 01:14:49,376
For now, she's fine.

1077
01:14:49,617 --> 01:14:51,373
And I'll take care of it.

1078
01:14:53,454 --> 01:14:55,091
How was the exam, today?

1079
01:14:55,331 --> 01:14:57,466
Good. The questions were easy.

1080
01:14:59,418 --> 01:15:00,462
Good.

1081
01:15:01,295 --> 01:15:03,466
Let's go, you'll be tired tomorrow.

1082
01:15:07,468 --> 01:15:08,809
Why don't you answer?

1083
01:15:09,011 --> 01:15:09,636
I'll call back later.

1084
01:15:09,637 --> 01:15:10,515
I'll call back later.

1085
01:15:11,305 --> 01:15:14,022
Your phone was on silent
when I called.

1086
01:15:14,308 --> 01:15:15,862
I was in surgery.

1087
01:15:16,060 --> 01:15:17,068
Dad...

1088
01:15:18,562 --> 01:15:20,650
I want you to talk to Mum.

1089
01:15:20,982 --> 01:15:22,025
Eliza,

1090
01:15:22,566 --> 01:15:25,652
what Mum and I
have to discuss is our business.

1091
01:15:25,653 --> 01:15:26,080
What Mum and I
have to discuss is our business.

1092
01:15:26,278 --> 01:15:27,322
No, Dad.

1093
01:15:27,530 --> 01:15:31,291
Don't think I can go home
like nothing happened.

1094
01:15:31,951 --> 01:15:33,790
Please go and talk to her.

1095
01:15:33,995 --> 01:15:36,130
Please, get your things.

1096
01:15:36,330 --> 01:15:37,292
- No, Dad.
- Eliza!

1097
01:15:37,498 --> 01:15:38,210
No!

1098
01:15:38,624 --> 01:15:41,721
Talk to her
or I won't sit the exam tomorrow.

1099
01:15:42,086 --> 01:15:42,168
Excuse me?

1100
01:15:42,169 --> 01:15:43,297
Excuse me?

1101
01:15:45,047 --> 01:15:46,340
I'm sorry.

1102
01:15:46,882 --> 01:15:48,436
I didn't mean it.

1103
01:15:49,176 --> 01:15:50,054
But...

1104
01:15:50,761 --> 01:15:54,605
please do it.
Go and talk to her tonight.

1105
01:15:55,474 --> 01:15:57,859
You think you can blackmail me?

1106
01:15:59,478 --> 01:16:03,489
Eliza! You think you're doing
this exam for me?

1107
01:16:03,691 --> 01:16:05,198
Or for your mother?

1108
01:16:05,776 --> 01:16:08,196
You think you're doing us a favour?

1109
01:16:09,071 --> 01:16:11,835
I jump through hoops for you
and you do this?

1110
01:16:12,033 --> 01:16:14,251
I never asked you to jump through-

1111
01:16:14,452 --> 01:16:14,701
No, you didn't.

1112
01:16:14,702 --> 01:16:15,876
No, you didn't.

1113
01:16:16,245 --> 01:16:20,302
But did you ask for any of the things
I always did for you?

1114
01:16:20,499 --> 01:16:23,180
Or did I just do them?

1115
01:16:24,503 --> 01:16:25,761
Can you even imagine

1116
01:16:25,963 --> 01:16:29,226
what we had to do
so you can live like this?

1117
01:16:31,552 --> 01:16:35,064
You shouldn't have done it
if it wasn't right.

1118
01:16:36,015 --> 01:16:39,479
It's so easy to say
"you shouldn't have done it".

1119
01:16:40,227 --> 01:16:42,778
Would you be going to study in the UK

1120
01:16:42,980 --> 01:16:45,365
without all the private lessons

1121
01:16:45,816 --> 01:16:47,734
or the competitions you were in?

1122
01:16:47,735 --> 01:16:47,949
Or the competitions you were in?

1123
01:16:48,152 --> 01:16:50,453
I hope you didn't rig those, too.

1124
01:16:50,655 --> 01:16:53,668
What? How can you say that?

1125
01:16:56,952 --> 01:16:59,254
How could you do this to Mum?

1126
01:17:00,748 --> 01:17:02,800
That's really not your business.

1127
01:17:04,126 --> 01:17:08,267
You know,
we made this effort for you.

1128
01:17:08,464 --> 01:17:10,136
So you wouldn't suffer.

1129
01:17:13,427 --> 01:17:15,978
I don't want to go to the UK anymore.

1130
01:17:16,180 --> 01:17:18,185
I want to stay here with Marius.

1131
01:17:18,599 --> 01:17:19,726
Really?

1132
01:17:20,184 --> 01:17:20,266
Very well then.

1133
01:17:20,267 --> 01:17:21,276
Very well then.

1134
01:17:22,395 --> 01:17:25,657
Go get a job,
see how the real world is.

1135
01:17:26,190 --> 01:17:29,405
But in 10 years
you might regret it.

1136
01:17:29,610 --> 01:17:31,331
It'll be too late.

1137
01:17:32,488 --> 01:17:34,873
- The lady needs the bathroom.
- OK.

1138
01:17:37,368 --> 01:17:39,207
Sleep here if you want.

1139
01:17:39,620 --> 01:17:41,423
I'll pick you up at 7.

1140
01:17:41,664 --> 01:17:43,171
Marius will take me.

1141
01:17:46,544 --> 01:17:47,635
Easy, Mum.

1142
01:17:48,754 --> 01:17:52,765
There now, dear.
I'm not dead yet.

1143
01:17:57,638 --> 01:17:58,765
Can you manage?

1144
01:17:59,056 --> 01:18:00,314
<i>Yes, dear.

1145
01:19:23,891 --> 01:19:24,983
Hi, Magda.

1146
01:19:25,184 --> 01:19:26,145
Hello.

1147
01:20:42,720 --> 01:20:43,681
Come in.

1148
01:20:48,059 --> 01:20:48,983
What's wrong?

1149
01:20:49,727 --> 01:20:53,239
Grandma collapsed
and Eliza got scared.

1150
01:20:53,522 --> 01:20:55,243
She's staying over.

1151
01:20:55,441 --> 01:20:57,909
- Is she OK now?
- She's better, yes.

1152
01:20:59,904 --> 01:21:01,576
How did she do in the exam?

1153
01:21:02,573 --> 01:21:04,625
I don't know, she didn't say.

1154
01:21:10,998 --> 01:21:13,134
She came to find me at Sandra's.

1155
01:21:16,128 --> 01:21:19,058
She was afraid Grandma would die
so she came.

1156
01:21:22,051 --> 01:21:23,522
You were at Sandra's?

1157
01:21:23,761 --> 01:21:24,686
Yes.

1158
01:21:27,348 --> 01:21:29,483
How did she know you were there?

1159
01:21:30,351 --> 01:21:31,608
I don't know.

1160
01:21:33,479 --> 01:21:35,199
And what did you tell her?

1161
01:21:35,940 --> 01:21:37,363
Nothing.

1162
01:21:38,943 --> 01:21:41,446
I promised her I'd talk to you.

1163
01:21:46,826 --> 01:21:49,506
You shouldn't have influenced her grade.

1164
01:21:50,871 --> 01:21:52,045
After that,

1165
01:21:52,957 --> 01:21:55,840
what does all we've taught her
count for?

1166
01:21:56,127 --> 01:21:57,799
The same as before.

1167
01:21:58,838 --> 01:22:00,594
But not here.

1168
01:22:06,846 --> 01:22:08,851
I'll follow her.

1169
01:22:09,640 --> 01:22:10,648
Where?

1170
01:22:11,308 --> 01:22:12,566
Anywhere.

1171
01:22:14,186 --> 01:22:15,989
Wherever she goes,

1172
01:22:16,689 --> 01:22:18,077
I'll go too.

1173
01:22:19,942 --> 01:22:21,994
Have you asked what she thinks?

1174
01:22:23,070 --> 01:22:24,363
I won't be in her way.

1175
01:22:25,364 --> 01:22:27,535
I'll cook for her...

1176
01:22:27,992 --> 01:22:29,712
I'll wait for her at home...

1177
01:22:30,036 --> 01:22:31,210
In the student dorm?

1178
01:22:31,746 --> 01:22:33,383
We'll rent somewhere.

1179
01:22:35,916 --> 01:22:37,304
With what?

1180
01:22:39,003 --> 01:22:41,589
We'll rent out this place,

1181
01:22:42,340 --> 01:22:43,893
or sell it.

1182
01:22:50,473 --> 01:22:52,893
Even if Eliza hadn't found out,

1183
01:22:53,100 --> 01:22:55,818
it was time for you to move.

1184
01:22:57,938 --> 01:22:59,944
Isn't this my home too?

1185
01:23:01,484 --> 01:23:03,156
Not for a long time.

1186
01:23:05,613 --> 01:23:09,125
Once Eliza leaves, you're free

1187
01:23:09,450 --> 01:23:11,918
to rebuild your life
with anyone you wish.

1188
01:23:12,495 --> 01:23:14,416
Rebuild what?

1189
01:23:15,414 --> 01:23:17,254
That no longer concerns me.

1190
01:23:18,709 --> 01:23:23,715
Just know that, whether Eliza
goes to the UK or to Cluj,

1191
01:23:24,548 --> 01:23:26,684
you can't stay here anymore.

1192
01:23:30,971 --> 01:23:32,858
May I ask you something?

1193
01:23:33,849 --> 01:23:37,397
Talk to Eliza,
get her to do the exam tomorrow.

1194
01:23:38,354 --> 01:23:39,611
Won't you drive her?

1195
01:23:40,356 --> 01:23:42,112
She said Marius would.

1196
01:23:45,236 --> 01:23:46,327
Fine.

1197
01:23:50,157 --> 01:23:52,957
But you stop sleeping here
from tonight.

1198
01:23:54,537 --> 01:23:56,756
I need to tell Eliza something.

1199
01:24:02,253 --> 01:24:03,261
OK.

1200
01:24:53,679 --> 01:24:56,230
They're doing the grille
tomorrow.

1201
01:24:57,224 --> 01:24:58,565
I'll deal with it.

1202
01:25:01,687 --> 01:25:03,075
Goodnight.

1203
01:25:04,231 --> 01:25:05,572
Goodnight.

1204
01:25:50,903 --> 01:25:52,624
- Morning.
- Hello, Elena.

1205
01:25:52,822 --> 01:25:55,242
Csilla wants
to see you urgently.

1206
01:25:55,449 --> 01:25:57,668
- She's here?
- She was called in.

1207
01:25:57,868 --> 01:25:58,996
Why?

1208
01:25:59,161 --> 01:26:01,249
She'll explain.
Coffee's ready.

1209
01:26:01,455 --> 01:26:02,713
Thank you.

1210
01:26:03,624 --> 01:26:06,839
- Is today the last exam?
- Yes, the last one.

1211
01:26:07,044 --> 01:26:09,014
- How's Eliza?
- Better.

1212
01:26:09,213 --> 01:26:10,934
God bless her.

1213
01:26:11,132 --> 01:26:12,223
Thank you.

1214
01:26:15,177 --> 01:26:16,388
What's going on?

1215
01:26:16,595 --> 01:26:18,019
Some prosecutors are here.

1216
01:26:18,222 --> 01:26:19,100
Why?

1217
01:26:19,306 --> 01:26:21,276
There's a warrant for Mr. Bulai.

1218
01:26:21,475 --> 01:26:25,070
The intern forbade them to see him
before you came.

1219
01:26:25,229 --> 01:26:28,492
- Why didn't you call me?
- Do you ever answer?

1220
01:26:29,942 --> 01:26:31,698
How is Bulai feeling?

1221
01:26:32,153 --> 01:26:33,873
Not so good, doctor.

1222
01:26:34,655 --> 01:26:36,707
- You offered them coffee?
- Yes.

1223
01:26:37,908 --> 01:26:40,079
Check if Eliza got to the exam.

1224
01:26:40,286 --> 01:26:41,923
- OK.
- Thank you.

1225
01:26:42,163 --> 01:26:44,666
Your car keys.
I'm taking it to be fixed.

1226
01:26:46,083 --> 01:26:47,886
Best of luck, doctor.

1227
01:26:48,169 --> 01:26:49,462
Thank you, Csilla.

1228
01:26:58,804 --> 01:27:00,145
Good morning.

1229
01:27:00,389 --> 01:27:01,481
Good morning.

1230
01:27:02,558 --> 01:27:05,144
Ivascu, Public Prosecutor's office.

1231
01:27:05,353 --> 01:27:07,025
My colleague, Mr. Albu.

1232
01:27:07,229 --> 01:27:09,815
- How may I help?
- Do you have a minute?

1233
01:27:10,024 --> 01:27:11,531
I have my rounds.

1234
01:27:11,734 --> 01:27:13,988
Still, sit.
We need to clarify a few things.

1235
01:27:14,195 --> 01:27:15,286
It won't take long.

1236
01:27:22,036 --> 01:27:23,210
I'm listening.

1237
01:27:23,537 --> 01:27:25,673
You know Mr. Alexandru Bulai?

1238
01:27:25,873 --> 01:27:27,380
He was admitted here.

1239
01:27:27,583 --> 01:27:28,508
Of course I do.

1240
01:27:28,709 --> 01:27:31,213
- How well?
- Not that well.

1241
01:27:31,420 --> 01:27:35,762
I don't mean you're friends
but you've met him before?

1242
01:27:36,008 --> 01:27:39,852
Sorry, but could you tell me
what this is about?

1243
01:27:41,389 --> 01:27:44,153
Mr. Bulai is facing criminal charges

1244
01:27:44,392 --> 01:27:47,239
regarding his function
<i>as</i> customs chief,

1245
01:27:47,478 --> 01:27:50,326
as well as other aspects
of his work.

1246
01:27:50,523 --> 01:27:51,816
I see.

1247
01:27:52,024 --> 01:27:53,032
And?

1248
01:27:53,234 --> 01:27:55,951
We'd like to discuss
some issues with him,

1249
01:27:56,153 --> 01:27:59,416
but his lawyer claims he's unfit.

1250
01:27:59,615 --> 01:28:00,826
Medically unfit.

1251
01:28:01,033 --> 01:28:02,504
He is very ill.

1252
01:28:03,160 --> 01:28:06,375
He'll die if he doesn't get
a liver very quickly.

1253
01:28:06,872 --> 01:28:09,257
And even then, his situation is...

1254
01:28:10,292 --> 01:28:13,341
I see.
So what do you recommend?

1255
01:28:13,754 --> 01:28:16,305
Do you think
he could stand detention?

1256
01:28:16,507 --> 01:28:19,141
Right now, it's out of the question.

1257
01:28:20,302 --> 01:28:21,595
But a talk?

1258
01:28:21,804 --> 01:28:23,358
Is that also too much?

1259
01:28:23,973 --> 01:28:25,693
Depends on how long it is.

1260
01:28:27,977 --> 01:28:29,400
Tell me,

1261
01:28:29,895 --> 01:28:32,066
would a medical commission

1262
01:28:32,314 --> 01:28:34,616
reach the same conclusion?

1263
01:28:34,859 --> 01:28:38,951
I presume so,
but since we live in Romania...

1264
01:28:39,155 --> 01:28:43,580
Doctors sometimes protect patients
for bad reasons...

1265
01:28:43,826 --> 01:28:45,748
Listen...

1266
01:28:46,287 --> 01:28:50,214
You see a mote in your brother's eye
but not the beam in your own.

1267
01:28:50,416 --> 01:28:52,753
Could you be more specific?

1268
01:28:53,085 --> 01:28:56,348
You have the reputation

1269
01:28:56,672 --> 01:28:58,594
of being an honest doctor.

1270
01:28:58,799 --> 01:29:02,430
You don't ask patients for incentives,
as some others do.

1271
01:29:02,636 --> 01:29:04,891
You're free to search my office-

1272
01:29:05,097 --> 01:29:07,352
There's no need for that,

1273
01:29:07,600 --> 01:29:10,613
and anyway, we'd need a warrant.

1274
01:29:11,479 --> 01:29:12,820
But you know...

1275
01:29:13,856 --> 01:29:15,742
Everyone has his weak spot.

1276
01:29:16,233 --> 01:29:17,954
I'm not sure I follow.

1277
01:29:19,236 --> 01:29:21,704
In very complex investigations,

1278
01:29:22,031 --> 01:29:25,329
certain procedures are followed,
do you understand?

1279
01:29:25,618 --> 01:29:30,541
Depending on the findings,
the charges can be extended.

1280
01:29:31,624 --> 01:29:34,838
Influence peddling,
incitement and so on.

1281
01:29:35,044 --> 01:29:37,844
So the suspect's calls
are intercepted.

1282
01:29:38,047 --> 01:29:39,257
Do you understand?

1283
01:29:39,715 --> 01:29:44,224
If any kind of fraud is suspected,
further investigations follow.

1284
01:29:44,387 --> 01:29:47,733
We know you had some conversations
with Mr. Bulai.

1285
01:29:49,517 --> 01:29:52,649
I greatly admire you, professionally.

1286
01:29:53,646 --> 01:29:56,778
And, though I may be
out of line here,

1287
01:29:56,982 --> 01:30:00,364
I'm sure my colleague here
and you above all

1288
01:30:00,569 --> 01:30:03,369
will keep this conversation confidential.

1289
01:30:04,615 --> 01:30:05,789
In brief,

1290
01:30:06,325 --> 01:30:09,422
everything you discussed
with Mr. Bulai

1291
01:30:09,620 --> 01:30:11,957
has been recorded and filed.

1292
01:30:15,376 --> 01:30:16,468
I see.

1293
01:30:18,212 --> 01:30:21,558
Excuse me if I'm being too blunt,

1294
01:30:22,091 --> 01:30:25,769
we're giving you the chance
to correct your mistakes.

1295
01:30:26,137 --> 01:30:29,102
"Errare humanum est",
as the Romans used to say.

1296
01:30:29,306 --> 01:30:32,854
You have mitigating circumstances.
We have children too.

1297
01:30:33,060 --> 01:30:36,275
We don't know
what we'd have done in your place.

1298
01:30:36,647 --> 01:30:38,154
But the law's the law.

1299
01:30:38,357 --> 01:30:40,327
He who persists in illegality

1300
01:30:40,568 --> 01:30:43,332
will probably have to pay for it.

1301
01:30:43,821 --> 01:30:46,834
As for Mr. Bulai,
with your permission,

1302
01:30:47,033 --> 01:30:49,666
we'd still like to talk to him today,

1303
01:30:49,869 --> 01:30:51,672
ask him a few questions.

1304
01:30:56,584 --> 01:30:58,256
That won't be possible.

1305
01:30:58,502 --> 01:30:59,427
Why?

1306
01:31:02,006 --> 01:31:05,683
Because I can't do that.
I hope you understand.

1307
01:31:09,055 --> 01:31:11,391
I'm very sorry to hear that, doctor.

1308
01:31:12,266 --> 01:31:13,773
I do understand.

1309
01:31:15,394 --> 01:31:17,530
And I respect your decision.

1310
01:31:18,814 --> 01:31:21,116
But I think you should reconsider.

1311
01:31:22,109 --> 01:31:24,909
These investigations
can be very unpleasant.

1312
01:31:25,154 --> 01:31:28,084
For your daughter too,
even if it's not her fault.

1313
01:31:29,200 --> 01:31:30,956
You're here at 10 tomorrow?

1314
01:31:31,285 --> 01:31:33,456
Tomorrow and any other day.

1315
01:31:34,205 --> 01:31:36,044
Then we'll see you tomorrow.

