01:55:26,971 --> 01:55:29,557
Can you look after Matei
in the morning?

1583
01:55:29,849 --> 01:55:33,195
I'm seeing a doctor,
I don't want him with me.

1584
01:55:35,396 --> 01:55:36,440
Of course.

1585
01:55:37,982 --> 01:55:41,862
There's a park nearby.
He won't be any trouble.

1586
01:55:43,988 --> 01:55:45,032
All right.

1587
01:55:54,373 --> 01:55:56,259
May I take him to school?

1588
01:55:57,918 --> 01:56:01,051
I'm going to Eliza's graduation.

1589
01:56:01,338 --> 01:56:02,466
Take him along.

1590
01:56:04,383 --> 01:56:05,854
Did you two make up?

1591
01:56:06,886 --> 01:56:08,013
I don't know.

1592
01:56:09,388 --> 01:56:10,599
It's difficult.

1593
01:56:11,557 --> 01:56:13,230
Children are like that.

1594
01:56:13,434 --> 01:56:15,854
Yes, you can never know.

1595
01:56:18,022 --> 01:56:20,193
I'll get the couch ready.

1596
01:56:20,649 --> 01:56:22,322
I'm dead tired.

1597
01:56:24,361 --> 01:56:26,201
- Thanks.
- It's OK.

1598
01:56:56,435 --> 01:56:58,238
You have to wait.

1599
01:56:58,437 --> 01:57:00,656
Only one child at a time!

1600
01:57:01,816 --> 01:57:04,402
Please tell your son he has to wait.

1601
01:57:04,610 --> 01:57:06,164
It's fine, madam.

1602
01:57:06,362 --> 01:57:07,915
The instructor said so.

1603
01:57:08,197 --> 01:57:10,202
It's not his responsibility.

1604
01:57:10,449 --> 01:57:11,873
Those are the rules.

1605
01:57:12,076 --> 01:57:16,335
If we apply those rules to kids
they'll never get their turn.

1606
01:57:16,539 --> 01:57:18,259
Maybe when they're older...

1607
01:57:18,457 --> 01:57:21,720
- Tell your son to wait!
- They're kids, lady!

1608
01:57:21,919 --> 01:57:24,007
- Matei!
- Don't throw stones!

1609
01:57:25,339 --> 01:57:26,762
Come over here.

1610
01:57:27,925 --> 01:57:30,310
- Really...
- I'm very sorry.

1611
01:57:30,636 --> 01:57:32,724
- No throwing.
- I apologize.

1612
01:57:32,930 --> 01:57:33,974
Did he hit you?

1613
01:57:35,599 --> 01:57:37,106
Why did you do that?

1614
01:57:37,309 --> 01:57:38,567
He should have waited.

1615
01:57:39,145 --> 01:57:40,568
That's true,

1616
01:57:40,813 --> 01:57:42,533
but you can't act like that.

1617
01:57:42,732 --> 01:57:43,859
Why?

1618
01:57:44,859 --> 01:57:46,994
That's no way to behave.

1619
01:57:47,361 --> 01:57:48,998
So how should I behave?

1620
01:57:50,948 --> 01:57:53,997
It's complicated.
Your mother will explain.

1621
01:57:54,702 --> 01:57:59,044
When you're with me,
never do that, all right?

1622
01:58:01,625 --> 01:58:02,587
Good.

1623
01:58:07,923 --> 01:58:09,893
Let's go, it's getting late.

1624
01:58:19,226 --> 01:58:20,982
Wait here for a moment.

1625
01:58:23,022 --> 01:58:24,612
Good morning, doctor.

1626
01:58:25,483 --> 01:58:26,776
Good morning.

1627
01:58:31,530 --> 01:58:32,788
Hello, Csilla.

1628
01:58:33,491 --> 01:58:34,665
Who's the woman?

1629
01:58:34,867 --> 01:58:36,374
Mr. Bulai's wife.

1630
01:58:36,577 --> 01:58:38,914
He had a heart attack this morning.

1631
01:58:40,122 --> 01:58:42,507
She's waiting to talk to you.

1632
01:58:43,626 --> 01:58:46,509
And the prosecutors are waiting
in my office.

1633
01:58:49,173 --> 01:58:50,015
I see.

1634
01:58:54,470 --> 01:58:55,597
Wish me luck.

1635
01:58:55,805 --> 01:58:57,276
Sok szerencsÃ©t.

1636
01:58:57,556 --> 01:58:58,944
That means luck?

1637
01:58:59,141 --> 01:59:00,268
It does.

1638
01:59:04,647 --> 01:59:06,734
I'm so sorry, madam.

1639
01:59:08,734 --> 01:59:10,953
Last night, my husband asked me

1640
01:59:11,237 --> 01:59:13,123
to give you this.

1641
01:59:13,447 --> 01:59:14,835
Madam...

1642
01:59:15,491 --> 01:59:17,876
Please.
It was his wish.

1643
01:59:21,455 --> 01:59:24,469
Thank you. Sorry for your loss.

1644
01:59:25,376 --> 01:59:27,677
Do you have your husband's ID?

1645
01:59:27,878 --> 01:59:28,721
Yes.

1646
01:59:28,921 --> 01:59:30,179
Come along, please.

1647
01:59:32,258 --> 01:59:33,349
Thank you.

1648
01:59:46,856 --> 01:59:48,113
Good morning.

1649
01:59:49,650 --> 01:59:51,406
Did you bring handcuffs?

1650
01:59:51,694 --> 01:59:54,659
Come on, doctor,
we're human too!

1651
01:59:55,614 --> 01:59:57,916
I got this now from Mr. Bulai.

1652
01:59:58,409 --> 02:00:00,295
Will you need it?

1653
02:00:01,495 --> 02:00:03,963
We're just doing our job, don't you see?

1654
02:00:04,165 --> 02:00:06,715
Yes. And it has to be done.

1655
02:00:07,460 --> 02:00:09,465
But you know what we say here:

1656
02:00:09,754 --> 02:00:11,889
No use excising the tumour if...

1657
02:00:12,673 --> 02:00:14,180
We do what we can.

1658
02:00:14,383 --> 02:00:16,602
Will you be here next week?

1659
02:00:16,802 --> 02:00:17,846
Where else?

1660
02:00:18,304 --> 02:00:21,981
Till Monday, then.
The investigation must continue.

1661
02:00:22,183 --> 02:00:23,310
I understand.

1662
02:00:23,809 --> 02:00:26,527
You'll always find me here.

1663
02:00:27,938 --> 02:00:30,572
But let's keep the kids out of it.

1664
02:00:32,777 --> 02:00:35,161
Sure. We'll see...

1665
02:00:36,405 --> 02:00:37,698
Have a good day.

1666
02:00:49,460 --> 02:00:50,421
Let's go.

1667
02:02:21,635 --> 02:02:22,810
Are you OK?

1668
02:02:29,351 --> 02:02:30,526
<i>Mafia.

1669
02:03:12,186 --> 02:03:13,527
Hello, Eliza.

1670
02:03:14,814 --> 02:03:15,775
Hello.

1671
02:03:16,524 --> 02:03:17,615
How are you?

1672
02:03:18,776 --> 02:03:19,784
Fine.

1673
02:03:20,778 --> 02:03:22,498
A bit nervous...

1674
02:03:24,281 --> 02:03:25,788
<i>Hows Mum'?

1675
02:03:26,659 --> 02:03:27,703
She's fine.

1676
02:03:28,369 --> 02:03:30,338
She won't bar the windows after all.

1677
02:03:30,538 --> 02:03:31,629
That's better.

1678
02:03:32,331 --> 02:03:33,209
Yes.

1679
02:03:33,833 --> 02:03:35,838
You get the results on Thursday?

1680
02:03:36,252 --> 02:03:37,130
Yes.

1681
02:03:38,754 --> 02:03:41,222
But I'm not sure I'll leave.

1682
02:03:42,508 --> 02:03:45,308
It would be a pity
but it's your decision.

1683
02:03:49,014 --> 02:03:51,316
Dad, about the exam...

1684
02:03:51,642 --> 02:03:52,686
Yes?

1685
02:03:55,354 --> 02:03:59,696
They let me write a bit longer
after the <i>3</i> hours were up.

1686
02:04:01,402 --> 02:04:02,612
<i>L</i> mean...

1687
02:04:03,487 --> 02:04:05,872
I started crying and they let me.

1688
02:04:08,075 --> 02:04:10,412
So I didn't need to do anything else.

1689
02:04:11,746 --> 02:04:13,038
I see.

1690
02:04:18,043 --> 02:04:19,930
Didn't I do well?

1691
02:04:26,302 --> 02:04:28,354
Can you take a photo? A keepsake?

1692
02:04:28,554 --> 02:04:29,515
Sure.

1693
02:04:41,275 --> 02:04:42,912
Look at me.

1694
02:04:44,695 --> 02:04:45,906
Smile!

1695
02:04:48,949 --> 02:04:50,421
Again...

1696
02:04:52,328 --> 02:04:53,716
Another smile...

1697
02:04:54,288 --> 02:04:55,581
Happier!
